{"alignment_id": "shijing__guofeng-yongfeng-007__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-yongfeng-007", "alignment_type": "exact_or_near_exact", "confidence": 0.99, "order": 2, "section_unit": "poem", "segment_type": "stanza", "alignment_granularity": "stanza", "is_coarse_alignment": false, "coarse_alignment_reason": null, "source_segment_count": 1, "target_segment_count": 1, "chinese_ref": "詩經·國風·鄘風·007.2", "chinese_text": "朝隮于西，崇朝其雨，女子有行，遠兄弟父母。", "translation_ref": "蝃蝀.2", "translation_text": "In the morning a rainbow rises in the west,\nAnd only during the morning is there rain.\nWhen a girl goes away from her home,\nShe separates from her brothers and parents."}
{"alignment_id": "shijing__guofeng-yongfeng-007__003__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-yongfeng-007", "alignment_type": "exact_or_near_exact", "confidence": 0.99, "order": 3, "section_unit": "poem", "segment_type": "stanza", "alignment_granularity": "stanza", "is_coarse_alignment": false, "coarse_alignment_reason": null, "source_segment_count": 1, "target_segment_count": 1, "chinese_ref": "詩經·國風·鄘風·007.3", "chinese_text": "乃如之人也，懷昏姻也，大無信也，不知命也。", "translation_ref": "蝃蝀.3", "translation_text": "This person\nHas her heart only on being married.\nGreatly is she untrue to herself,\nAnd does not recognize the law of her lot."}
